            <iframe name="ifr-meteo" src="https://www.meteoblue.com/en/weather/widget/daily/brașov_romania_683844?geoloc=fixed&days=7&tempunit=C&windunit=kmh&precipunit=mm&layout=image"></iframe>
            
            <p>Verifică mai multe detalii pe <a href="https://www.meteoblue.com/en/weather/week/brașov_romania_683844" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">MeteoBlue</a>.</p>

